Line68.EC212: After Lorath’s performance last night, I wager he’ll want to know.
VoiceDir66.EC212: Recounting the rumor. Casual. Could be something, could be nothing.
Line66.EC212: Rumor has it a pale man passed through the Abahru Canyons some time ago. Fearsome fellow, dressed in black.
VoiceDir49.EC212: Tired. Mildly annoyed with Lorath. Glad to have some news, at least.
Line49.EC212: (sigh) No. No word from Orbei. Same as yesterday and the day before, but...I have something else.
